title: Dough. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2016)
description:
In theaters: April 29th, 2016

Description:

Jonathan Pryce (Pirates of the Caribbean, Game of Thrones) and Pauline Collins (Shirley Valentine) star in this hilarious new comedy that shows you don't have to be baked to make some Dough! An old Jewish baker (Pryce) takes on a young Muslim apprentice (Jerome Holder) to save his failing London kosher bakery. When his apprentice's marijuana stash accidentally falls in the mixing dough, the challah starts flying off the shelves! Dough is a warmhearted and humorous story about overcoming prejudice and finding redemption in unexpected places.

Director: John Goldschmidt

Writers: Yehuda Jez Freedman, Jonathan Benson

Actors: Jonathan Pryce, Pauline Collins, Jerome Holder, Philip Davis, Ian Hart, Malachi Kirby, Andrew Ellis, Natasha Gordon, Melanie Freeman, Daniel Caltagirone

Genre: Comedy, Drama

Run Time: 1 hour 34 minutes
